msgid "<strong>Appointment booking <strong>🗓️</strong></strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Booking af aftaler <strong>🗓️</strong></strong>"

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Assign Personnel</strong>: Assign maintenance tasks to specific "
"employees or teams, ensuring that the right person is handling the repair."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Tildel personale</strong>: Tildel vedligeholdelsesopgaver til "
"specifikke medarbejdere eller teams, så den rette person altid udfører "
"reparationen."

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Automate Your Reordering Process 🚀</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Automatisér din genbestillingsproces 🚀</strong>"

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Check Stock Levels</strong>:"
msgstr "<strong>Kontrollér lagerbeholdninger</strong>:"

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Choose Your Vendors</strong>: Select the vendors you want to reorder"
" from. You can also add bulk pricing options to save time and money."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Vælg din leverandør</strong>: Vælg de leverandører, du vil "
"genbestille fra, og tilføj eventuelt mængderabatter for at spare tid og "
"penge."

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Confirm Orders</strong>: When an order is confirmed, a delivery is automatically created in the Inventory app. This allows you to keep track of stock levels and ensure you have enough inventory for your daily\n"
"                        operations."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Bekræft ordrer</strong>: Når en ordre bekræftes, oprettes der "
"automatisk en levering i Lagerappen. Det giver dig mulighed for at følge "
"lagerbeholdningen og sikre, at der altid er tilstrækkeligt lager til de "
"daglige\n"
"                        aktiviteter."

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Create Maintenance Requests</strong>: Easily generate maintenance "
"requests when equipment needs repair or servicing. These requests can be "
"categorized and prioritized based on urgency."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Opret vedligeholdelsesanmodninger</strong>: Generér hurtigt "
"vedligeholdelsesanmodninger, når udstyr skal repareres eller serviceres. "
"Anmodningerne kan kategoriseres og prioriteres efter hastighed."

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Create Reordering Rules</strong>: Click on the Products menu and "
"select Reordering Rules. Here, you can set minimum and maximum quantities "
"for each product to trigger automatic reordering."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Opret genbestillingsregler</strong>: Gå til menuen \"Produkter\", og "
"vælg \"Genbestillingsregler\". Her kan du angive minimums- og "
"maksimumsmængder for hvert produkt, som automatisk udløser genbestilling."

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Create Tailor-Made Subscriptions and Sell Products Effortlessly "
"🛒</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Opret skræddersyede abonnementer, og sælg produkter nemt og uden "
"besvær. 🛒</strong>"

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Define Equipment</strong>: Create detailed profiles for each piece "
"of equipment, including specifications, usage history,emplacement,  and "
"maintenance requirements."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Definér udstyr</strong>: Opret detaljerede profiler for hvert "
"udstyr, inklusive vejledninger, brugshistorik, placering og "
"vedligeholdelsesbehov."

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Effortlessly manage your Point of Sale 💵</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Nem håndtering af dit kassesystem 💵</strong>"

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Effortlessly manage your eCommerce 💵</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Nem håndtering af din e-Handel 💵</strong>"

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Equipment Definition and Maintenance Requests</strong> 🛠️🔧"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Definition af udstyr og vedligeholdelsesanmodninger</strong> 🛠️🔧"

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>If you want to execute a practical guided tour of this module, you "
"should Import demo data and try the features described in this "
"article.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Hvis du vil gennemføre en praktisk, guidet tur i dette modul, skal "
"du importere demodata og prøve de funktioner, der er beskrevet i "
"artiklen.</strong>"

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Integration with Employee Management</strong>: Link maintenance "
"tasks to employee schedules, ensuring efficient allocation of resources."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Integration med medarbejderadministration</strong>: Kobl "
"vedligeholdelsesopgaver til medarbejdernes tidsplaner for at sikre en "
"effektiv ressourcefordeling."

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Navigate to the Inventory App</strong>: Go to the Inventory app in "
"Odoo."
msgstr "<strong>Navigér til Lagerappen</strong>: Gå til Lagerappen i Odoo."

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Resupply as Needed</strong>: If stock levels are low, create a "
"purchase order from the Purchase app. Link it to the right vendor to ensure "
"timely replenishment."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Genopfyld efter behov</strong>: Hvis lagerbeholdningen er lav, kan "
"du oprette en indkøbsordre i Indkøbsappen. Knyt den til den rette leverandør "
"for at sikre rettidig genopfyldning."

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Scheduling and Resource Allocation 🏋️‍♂️</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Tildeling af planlægning og ressourcer 🏋️‍♂️</strong>"

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Set Up Automatic Reordering</strong>:"
msgstr "<strong>Konfigurér automatisk genbestilling</strong>:"

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Thanks</strong> to the invoicing policy that you can modify, the "
"generated invoice is always the reflect of the reality on the field and it "
"is fair for the customer."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Takket</strong> være den faktureringspolitik, du kan tilpasse, "
"stemmer den udstedte faktura altid overens med det faktiske forbrug og er "
"fair for kunden."

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Track Progress</strong>: Monitor the status of maintenance requests "
"in real-time, from creation to completion, ensuring nothing falls through "
"the cracks."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Følg fremskridt</strong>: Overvåg status for "
"vedligeholdelsesanmodninger i realtid, fra oprettelse til afslutning, og "
"sørg for, at intet bliver overset."

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"A free, personalized, integrated <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Website</font></strong> in a few clicks. Start receiving orders directly in Odoo and go live with your \n"
"                <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">E-shop</font></strong> in a few minutes."
msgstr ""
"En gratis, personlig og integreret <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\""
">hjemmeside</font></strong> på få klik. Modtag ordrer direkte i Odoo, og få "
"din\n"
"                <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">netbutik</font></"
"strong> online på få minutter."

